data.description: Gorgeous and completely updated Eichler home has all the features you expect to see in this California Modern style—open living spaces, large windows allowing an abundance of natural light, atrium at the center of this home and so much more! This home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, 1795 square feet on a .17  acre lot. Newly sealed modern vinyl flooring and fresh paint throughout. Open concept kitchen includes newer cabinets, quartz counters, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and large island. A beautiful tile fireplace anchors the living room, complete with large floor to ceiling windows overlooking private backyard with fig and citrus trees. Primary retreat includes plenty of light,  en-suite bath with modern vanity, walk-in tile shower with subway tile, and spacious closet. Schools: Westwood Elementary,  El Dorado Middle, Concord High School.
